{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_tqt","exhibition_name":"展览二区","location":"509,706","name":"听琴图","size":"宋 纵92cm，横36cm","like":5,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=88","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_tqt","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"宋徽宗赵佶，公元1082年至公元1135年，宋朝第八位皇帝，在绘画领域颇有造诣。这幅画的背景和道具处理地十分简练，主人公背后画松树一株，女萝攀附，枝叶扶疏，亭亭如盖。松下有竹数竿，摇曳多姿。道具除琴案外，仅一几，几上置薰炉，香烟袅袅。主人公对面，设小巧玲珑山石一块，上有一小古鼎，中插花枝一束，除以上这些外，别无它物。所有布景、道具以及次要人物的位置，都围绕着主人公的演奏而安排。整个画面的气氛，仿佛在这静谧之中，有一阵阵琴声，混合着微风吹动松枝竹叶之声，从画中传出。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB3_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB31_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB32_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB33_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB34_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/qJBZ1EqB35_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/TfwvIqOfBR.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}